{"tid":439893,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"作客馬里博爾大屠殺　紅軍破多項紀錄","createTime":"2017-10-18T08:41:14.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-18T12:53:52.000Z","uid":31798,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"26400649e132ddb11b50bd3d36e7ea5d3568d5e9","tid":439893,"uid":31798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T08:41:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20171018&amp;s=7032049&amp;a=57345873\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20171018%26s%3D7032049%26a%3D57345873&d=3l%2FqZyfP6LRDkR2YTTFA02i1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=18778c9a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20171018%26s%3D7032049%26a%3D57345873&h=5bf8c9c1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20171018&amp;s=7032049&amp;a=57345873</a><br />\n作客馬里博爾大屠殺　紅軍破多項紀錄<br />\n<br />\n利物浦喺歐聯分組賽作客斯文尼亞球隊馬里博爾大炒對手7:0，平咗歐聯客場最大勝仗紀錄，同佢哋自己同皇家馬德里共同保持嘅歐聯最大勝仗紀錄8:0只差一球，不過，紅軍喺今次「大屠殺」亦刷咗隊史以至英格蘭球隊紀錄。<br />\n<br />\n利物浦喺2007年11月6號主場以8:0狂數比錫達斯，創出歐聯最大勝使紀錄，其後皇馬喺2015年12月主場對馬模亦以8:0贏出而平咗利記紀錄。至於利物浦今場大勝馬里博爾，係歐聯第九場贏7:0嘅比賽，但以客場計就係第三支可以贏到7:0嘅球隊，之前兩隊分別係2010年11月作客大勝斯洛伐克球隊日利納嘅馬賽，以及2014年10月以7:0炒白俄羅斯球隊巴迪而平呢個客場紀錄嘅薩克達。<br />\n<br />\n今場比賽，利物浦打破咗隊史喺歐洲賽事嘅客場最大勝仗紀錄，亦係第一支喺歐聯（包括前身歐冠盃）客場贏到7:0嘅英格蘭球隊。紅軍之前曾經三次喺歐戰客場贏5:0，分別係1964年對冰島嘅雷克雅維克、1976年對北愛球隊十字軍同埋2001年對芬蘭嘅夏卡。"},{"pid":"2ea9814c9332f00be7efda088fe4983541822b4c","tid":439893,"uid":119494,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T08:45:06.000Z","msg":"之前笑利記果班粉腸呢？話利記無資格打歐聯班粉腸去左邊呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00cf97fbed3f2af9936bfcefddbcc711c8d8bc0a","tid":439893,"uid":33770,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T08:47:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>之前笑利記果班粉腸呢？話利記無資格打歐聯班粉腸去左邊呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n炒垃圾都有得吹奏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93d2b1f9f68c33345989e89a3c7b75b5ba7ad527","tid":439893,"uid":4492,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T08:48:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>之前笑利記果班粉腸呢？話利記無資格打歐聯班粉腸去左邊呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n炒垃圾都有得吹奏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我地曼聯對呢隊起碼炒雙位數啦"},{"pid":"49d78ab5a521f40f780a8645e36a396df37c7847","tid":439893,"uid":56212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T08:49:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>之前笑利記果班粉腸呢？話利記無資格打歐聯班粉腸去左邊呀<img src=\"/asse